  "page": "Master of the Tower of Glimmering",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Master of the Tower of Glimmering</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafhotho_harlaw.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafhotho_harlaw.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> is a title held by the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_the_Tower_of_Glimmering\" title=\"House Harlaw of the Tower of Glimmering\">House Harlaw of the Tower of Glimmering</a>, the ruler of the <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_Glimmering\" title=\"Tower of Glimmering\">Tower of Glimmering</a> on <a href=\"/index.php/Harlaw\" title=\"Harlaw\">Harlaw</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Masters_of_the_Tower_of_Glimmering\">Known Masters of the Tower of Glimmering</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Master_of_the_Tower_of_Glimmering&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Masters of the Tower of Glimmering\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Master <a href=\"/index.php/Hotho_Harlaw\" title=\"Hotho Harlaw\">Hotho Harlaw</a>, the current Master of the Tower of Glimmering.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\